description:
Requirements: Android 2.0.1+
Overview: Dive into the world of Paper Monsters and watch a living world made out of paper, cardboard, and a few cotton balls unfold right before your eyes
Paper Monsters takes all of the classic 2d platforming elements, combines them with cutting edge graphics and then packs it onto your mobile device!


The hit game that USA TODAY calls a real treat is now on Kindle Fire!

